          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5">This shift aligns with evolving US regulations under President Trump, who aims to position the US as a global crypto leader. Citadel’s expertise could enhance market stability and risk management. Meanwhile, EDX Markets, backed by Citadel and Fidelity, is expanding in Singapore.</p>
